data.description: HOME SWEET HOME! You are instantly welcomed by the charming front porch and once inside the list goes on! The kitchen overlooks the quiet backyard that focuses on a fully fenced oversized yard, perfect for your morning coffee or evening barbecue. All STAINLESS STEEL KITCHEN appliances included and large kitchen pantry. IN HOUSE separate laundry room UPSTAIRS. Downstairs guest bath. Upstairs there are 4 generous sized bedrooms. The master suite is waiting for you and it is HUGE! Bathroom features a GARDEN TUB, separate shower and large walk-in closet. This lovely two-story could be yours if you hurry! NO HOA!
